domain id is passed in URL;
requires admin sign-in

restricted-domains -- 
Get info about all restricted domains;
requires admin sign-in

restricted-domains/{restricted_domain_id} -- 
edit info about a given restricted domain;
domain id is passed in URL;
data to edit listed in params;
requires admin sign-in

