requires admin sign-in

routes -- 
get a list of all available routes;
requires admin sign-in

v1/admin/users/{user_uid}/app_passwords -- 
get a list of app passwords for a given user;
user is passed in the URL;
requires admin sign-in

v1/admin/users/{user_uid}/app_passwords -- 
Delete all app passwords for a given user;
user is passed in the URL;
requires admin sign-in

memberships -- 
Add a given user as a member of a given project;
information is provided in the body;
requires an admin sign-in

usage -- 
get information about site usage over time;
Does not require sign-in

usage/latest -- 
get the latest set of information about site usage;
Does not require sign-in

user_policies/{policy_code} -- 
Post a Contact Us email;
Contact data is passed in Body;
Does not require user sign-in

user_policies/{policy_code} -- 
Post a Security Incident email;
Contact data is passed in Body;
Adds key/value pair topic=security (otherwise is the same as sending a contact message)
Does not require user sign-in

policies/{policy_code} -- 
get information about a given policy;
policy_code is passed in URL

user_policies/{policy_code} -- 
get the signed-in user's status with regard to a given policy;
policy_code is passed in URL

user_policies/{policy_code} -- 
get the signed-in user's status with regard to a given policy;
policy_code is passed in URL;
accept_flag value (1) is passed in Body

v1/app_passwords -- 
Create a new App Password for the signed in user;
App Password label is passed in the Body

v1/app_passwords/{app_password_uuid} -- 
Get information about a given one of the signed in user's App Passwords;
app_password_uuid is passed in URL

v1/app_passwords/{app_password_uuid} -- 
Edit the label for a specific one of the signed-in User's App Passwords;
app_password_uuid is passed in URL;
new label is in params

v1/app_passwords/{app_password_uuid} -- 
