app_password_uuid is passed in the URL

environment -- 
get the SWAMP environment from the .env file;
Does not require sign-in

assessment_runs/check_compatibility -- 
Check if elements in an assessment tripple are incompatible;
Package, Tool, and Platform Version are provided in the body;
seems to only check package/platform incompatibility

assessment_runs/{assessment_run_uuid} -- 
Get information about a given Assessment Run;
assessment_run_uuid is passed in URL;
not used in SWAMP UI

assessment_runs/{assessment_run_uuid} -- 
Get information about a given Assessment Run;
assessment_run_uuid is passed in URL;
edit parameters are passed in params;
not used in SWAMP UI

assessment_runs/{assessment_run_uuid} -- 
Delete a given Assessment Run;
assessment_run_uuid is passed in URL

assessment_runs/{assessment_run_uuid}/run_requests -- 
Get information about a given Assessment Run;
assessment_run_uuid is passed in URL

run_requests/one-time -- 
run one or more given assessments;
Creates an assessment _run_request record linking the given assessment_run(s) with the one-time run_request;
Given assessment are provided in the Body (multiple can be included as an array)

run_requests/{run_request_uuid} -- 
Create an assessment_run_request record (scheduled assessment) for the given run_request (schedule container) and the given assessment_run(s);
Given run_request_uuid is passed in the URL;
Given assessment are provided in the Body (multiple can be included as an array)

run_requests/{run_request_uuid} -- 
Get information about a given run_request record (schedule container);
Given run_request_uuid is passed in the URL

run_requests/{run_request_uuid} -- 
Edit a Run Request (Schedule container);
run_request_uuid is passed in the URL;
project, name, and descriptions are in the params

run_requests/{run_request_uuid}/assessment_runs/{assessment_run_uuid} -- 
Delete the assessment_run_request (scheduled assessment) for a given Run Request (Schedule container) and assessment_run;
run_request_uuid and assessment_run_uuid are passed in the URL

run_requests/{run_request_uuid} -- 
Delete a given Run Request (Schedule container);
run_request_uuid is passed in the URL

run_request_schedules -- 
Create Run Request Schedules (individual schedules) for the signed in user associated with the given Project;
An array of schedules with Run Request, type, and time of day is in the body;
Must be set in Postman as raw json array;
Need to post a run_request first;
Note that this adds to any existing run_request_schedules for a run_request

run_request_schedules/{run_request_schedule_uuid} -- 
Get information about a given run_request_schedule record (scheduled time);
Given run_request_schedule_uuid is passed in the URL

run_request_schedules/run_requests/{run_request_uuid} -- 
Get information about a the run_request_schedule records (scheduled times) in a given run_request (schedule container);
Given run_request_uuid is passed in the URL

run_request_schedules/{run_request_schedule_uuid} -- 
Edit information about a given run_request_schedule record (scheduled time);
Given run_request_schedule_uuid is passed in the URL;
Edited info in params;
Not used in SWAMP UI

run_request_schedules -- 
Edit All Run Request Schedules (individual schedules) for a Run Requst;
An array of schedules with Run Request Schedule, Run Request, type, day, and time of day is in the params;
Must be set in Postman as raw json array in Body;

run_request_schedules/{run_request_schedule_uuid} -- 
Delete a given run_request_schedule record (scheduled time);
Given run_request_schedule_uuid is passed in the URL;
Edited info in params;
Not used in SWAMP UI

