packages/versions/{package_version_uuid}/directory-list --
Get a list of the directories in a given directory of a package version archive;
package_version_uuid is passed in URL;
Set dirname in params

packages/versions/{package_version_uuid}/directory-tree --
Get a directory tree for a given directory of a package version archive;
package_version_uuid is passed in URL;
